---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Qualiber"
  description="How Qualiber LLC handles information submitted through qualiber.ai."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/">
        <svg class="mark" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="5" cy="6" r="2.4" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"></circle>
          <circle cx="5" cy="18" r="2.4" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"></circle>
          <circle cx="19" cy="12" r="3" fill="#35D0A5"></circle>
          <path d="M6.8 7 16.4 11M6.8 17 16.4 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" opacity="0.55"></path>
        </svg>
        Qualiber
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">← Back to site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="wrap prose">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: 20 July 2026</p>

    <p>This site, <strong>qualiber.ai</strong>, is operated by <strong>Qualiber&nbsp;LLC</strong> ("Qualiber", "we", "us"). This policy explains what information we collect through the site and how we use it. We keep it deliberately short because the site does very little with your data.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>The only information we collect is what you choose to enter in our contact / demo-request form: your <strong>name</strong>, <strong>work email</strong>, <strong>company</strong>, and an optional <strong>message</strong>. We do not require an account, and we do not ask for sensitive personal information.</p>

    <h2>How the form works</h2>
    <p>Form submissions are processed by <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy/" rel="noopener">Formspree</a>, a third-party service that delivers the message to our inbox. Their handling of the data is governed by their own privacy policy. We receive the submission by email and use it solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>

    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <p>We use your information to reply to your request, schedule a demo, and follow up about Qualiber and Qualgraph. We do not sell your information, and we do not share it except with the service providers needed to operate this site and communicate with you.</p>

    <h2>Analytics &amp; cookies</h2>
    <p>This site does not set advertising cookies or sell tracking data. Your theme preference is stored only in your browser's local storage and never leaves your device. If we add privacy-respecting analytics in the future, we will update this policy.</p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>You can ask us to access or delete the information you submitted at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@qualiber.ai">hello@qualiber.ai</a>. We keep inquiry records only as long as needed to follow up or as required for our records.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@qualiber.ai">hello@qualiber.ai</a>.</p>

    <p style="margin-top:2.5rem;"><a class="backlink" href="/">← Back to qualiber.ai</a></p>
  </main>
</Base>
